ve your application every chance you should clearly show the need for the project, how many people will benefit, and whether it can be delivered well. Value for money is also important.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_toggle][et_pb_toggle title=&#8221;I have some money for my project from another funder, but need more. Can I apply to you?&#8221; open_toggle_text_color=&#8221;#09598E&#8221; open_toggle_background_color=&#8221;#FFFFFF&#8221; closed_toggle_background_color=&#8221;#FFFFFF&#8221; icon_color=&#8221;#09598E&#8221; toggle_icon=&#8221;&#x4c;||divi||400&#8243; use_icon_font_size=&#8221;on&#8221; icon_font_size=&#8221;32px&#8221; open_icon_color=&#8221;#09598E&#8221; open_toggle_icon=&#8221;&#x4b;||divi||400&#8243; open_use_icon_font_size=&#8221;on&#8221; open_icon_font_size=&#8221;32px&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; title_text_color=&#8221;#09598E&#8221; title_level=&#8221;h3&#8243; title_font_size=&#8221;21px&#8221; border_radii=&#8221;on|12px|12px|12px|12px&#8221; border_width_all=&#8221;0px&#8221; box_shadow_style=&#8221;preset1&#8243; box_shadow_color=&#8221;rgba(0,0,0,0.1)&#8221; locked=&#8221;off&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Yes. We are happy to be a match funder to help make your project happen.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_toggle][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_toggle title=&#8221;I don&#8217;t have an organisation set up yet. Are you able to pay the grant to individuals? &#8221; open_toggle_text_color=&#8221;#09598E&#8221; open_toggle_background_color=&#8221;#FFFFFF&#8221; closed_toggle_background_color=&#8221;#FFFFFF&#8221; icon_color=&#8221;#09598E&#8221; toggle_icon=&#8221;&#x4c;||divi||400&#8243; use_icon_font_size=&#8221;on&#8221; icon_font_size=&#8221;32px&#8221; open_icon_color=&#8221;#09598E&#8221; open_toggle_icon=&#8221;&#x4b;||divi||400&#8243; open_use_icon_